@baseUrl = http://localhost:4023
@token = REPLACE_WITH_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Store details (used on invoices and GST reports)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stores
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update a store (ADMIN)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/stores/REPLACE_WITH_STORE_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Shr-x Collections",
  "phone": "911234567890",
  "address": "MG Road, Bengaluru, Karnataka",
  "gstin": "29ABCDE1234F1Z5",
  "footerNote": "Thank you for shopping with Shr-x ERP"
}

### Loyalty lookup (for POS customer)
GET {{baseUrl}}/loyalty?phone=9123456789
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
